{"tid":2223092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍無人機隊人員臂章現中國地圖  《環球時報》社論︰是極其囂張的挑釁","createTime":"2020-09-29T14:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T08:18:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":210,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"7f834ba6ea0fd5facc570c1f5bfb21d2ce5f290a","tid":2223092,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T14:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/8e1b5b21e700e263c11f07f0123755c3/2020/09/e1965c74e206c0c685f5bfa286d8879b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2F8e1b5b21e700e263c11f07f0123755c3%2F2020%2F09%2Fe1965c74e206c0c685f5bfa286d8879b.jpg&h=e1ce33bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》社論批評，指軍隊的日常訓練有假想敵並非很奇怪的事，但臂章印有中國國旗圖案，是極其囂張的挑釁。 <br />\n<br />\n社論指，美國空軍對上一次將一個國家的地圖印到臂章上，是在越戰，臂章印上中國地圖已很激進，而照片曝光不可能是錯誤操作，美軍顯然是要藉此傳遞強烈信號，社論認為此舉是試探美國及國際社會反應，提高美國與國際輿論對這種敵對的接受度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2359500\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2359500&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWHr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=2f27bd71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2359500</a>"},{"pid":"9934144921c07bd573b59b2732987c2f3e464253","tid":2223092,"uid":33099,"like":224,"dislike":1,"score":223,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T14:13:57.000Z","msg":"人地都係跟你忠誠勇毅學野 貼到周身都係"},{"pid":"84c2215a153c9ed73db0fd2950165f5557ddfb26","tid":2223092,"uid":136431,"like":116,"dislike":2,"score":114,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T14:14:16.000Z","msg":"面對挑釁，一定要反擊！<br />\n支那加油！"},{"pid":"160f368a68e812a8c7ee4e7c296d0eceb99642da","tid":2223092,"uid":80624,"like":145,"dislike":2,"score":143,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T14:14:36.000Z","msg":"咁你之前又炸人關島<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d010a9d3f178bd97b94c9a076f5d7dc5dd66ec6a","tid":2223092,"uid":146285,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T14: